headline: KBRA Releases Research – Seized but Not Lost: Insurance Proceeds and Aviation ABS
summary: NEW YORK, August 28, 2025--KBRA releases research evaluating the impact of insurance settlements between international insurers and aviation lessors on the aviation asset-backed securities (ABS) sector.

headline: 3 Reasons to Avoid AIG and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: AIG has been treading water for the past six months, holding steady at $83. The stock also fell short of the S&P 500’s 8.8% gain during that period.
